item.title: Muriel Bowser bio
item.description: know more about Gov Muriel Bowser Muriel Bowser is committed to making sure every Washingtonian gets a fair shot in a growing and prosperous Washington, DC. Her administration is focused on making DC’s prosperity more inclusive, advancing DC values, and building safer, stronger, and healthier neighborhoods across DC’s eight wards. Washington, DC is unique in the American political system – the mayor, DC’s chief executive, functions as a governor, county executive, and mayor.
